00:00:42.020 --> 00:00:46.520
mixtures as you know, and we'll talk about
some of the ramifications of that as his paintings age.

00:00:46.580 --> 00:00:51.920
Argendiego asks about how to increase the
canvas tension after painting on it with a

00:00:51.960 --> 00:00:57.080
palette knife, stretching a canvas having a nice taut
surface, losing some of that tautness by scraping, etc.

00:00:57.080 --> 00:00:57.760
How do you get it back?

00:00:57.760 --> 00:00:59.360
I have a couple of good ideas for you.

00:00:59.360 --> 00:01:01.940
