00:01:01.940 --> 00:01:06.000
In fact, we touched on this a bit last time, but it's a really important question.

00:01:06.060 --> 00:01:08.390
In fact, you can't do anything but paint like yourself

00:01:08.390 --> 00:01:09.390
as much as you might try.

00:01:09.390 --> 00:01:13.409
Anyway, we'll delve back into that and explore
that in a little bit more depth.

00:01:13.409 --> 00:01:16.900
